20 executive director of the Office of Administrative Services; and
21 b. Division of Management Services, which shall be headed by a
22 director who shall be appointed by the commissioner of the
23 Department of Kentucky State Police and who shall report to the
24 executive director of the Office of Administrative Services;
25 2. Office of Operations, which shall be headed by an executive director
26 who shall be appointed by the commissioner of the Department of
27 Kentucky State Police and who shall report to the commissioner;
