5 matters in which there is a suspicion of violation of written policy,
6 administrative regulation, or statutory law within the Department of
7 Public Advocacy only when the investigation will have no prejudicial
8 impact upon a person who has an existing attorney-client relationship
9 with the Department of Public Advocacy. Notwithstanding the
